
lesson 13 A1 level



usually use for voiting.
another usage is for feature verbs.

I shall go there.
We shall eat something.

__only use with "I" and "We".

Shall I visit her family?
Shall we buy a house?

What shall I do?

We shan't sit there. == We shall not sit there.
I shan't ask Maryam. == I shall not ask Maryam.

